{
  "stem": "9943.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I went with this-- with this friends to-- to Odessa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we are going back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now he wants to stay in Kiev, and I want to go to a quiet place where I can recover the-- the war, because I was pregnant at that time.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I found out that I'm pregnant, and I wanted to be in a place which is calm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have a choice because they know me at the Ministry of Health, so they gave me an assignment in Pereiaslav-- Pereiaslav, P-E-Y-I-A-S-L-A-V, Pereiaslav.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's near Kiev.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's near the Dnieper.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's not so near Kiev, as it's near the Dnieper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there's-- they don't have any industry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They don't have a train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In other words, I asked for such an assignment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got it, and we are in Kiev.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it-- we are a week, and during this week, the police was taking us several times to the police, because we looked dressed differently than the Russians, and they were concerned about the fifth column, about spies.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we are taken to the police and-- to give the account, why and what and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that finally, we took a boat and went to Pereiaslav and started to work in Pereiaslav.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Pereiaslav, I found myself that my abdomen is getting bigger than the pregnancy, because I figured more or less that I might be pregnant two months, two and a half months, and it looks like six months.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had to go to a committee, and I start to tell them that I'm pregnant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they thought that probably I would have to have an operation, a laparotomy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It means they'd open the-- they would have to open the belly, because they didn't think that it was a pregnancy.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
